        <detaileddescription>
<para>Implementations should check the <ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1gameloop_1abdb94a899ecc215ffa46e24880ebd8ec" kindref="member">CommitPoint</ref> flags and perform the appropriate synchronization actions. The order of operations should be:</para>
